    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000606/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """The main objective is course is to gain knowledge of the basic fabrication methods, structure and properties of materials for energy management, with a particular emphasis on measuring techniques and performance indicators in electrochemical energy storage.
Masterclasses combined with Laboratory practices are scheduled in order to expand the knowledge of the students in materials for energy ."""@es ;
