<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000606/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Continuum assessment
Only if the whole class attendance > 60% of the days
Final mark = PE1 (40%) + PE2 (60%)
PE1: partial examination 1
PE2: partial examination 2
Pass mark: (PE1 + PE2)/2 > 5

Final Exam
Final exam with a total weight of 100%
Pass mark: Final Exam > 5"""@es ;
